 l\, Danish Composers' Society / Dansk Komponistforening\, and Koda Kultur)
 \nLocation: Struer\, Denmark\nAward: DKK 30\,000 work grant (~EUR 4\,000) 
 + private studio + accommodation in Sound Art Lab's artist apartment + ful
